{"tid":1357374,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發即日］連登女神慘遭戴帽！！","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:04:34.000Z","uid":20948,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5567c698024d55f42b3c61439881281a164f739b","tid":1357374,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uRYgk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uRYgk2.png&h=ee215a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家支持超安全運動！！！<br />\n幫手推推呢個post！<br />\n<br />\n今日已經見到有人戴頭盔返工！唔好俾佢停！香港人要保護好自己！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要推呢啲行動係有難度，特別係平時著西裝返工嘅手足，但香港警察已經沒有維持治安保護市民嘅能力！<br />\n大家必須要保護好自己！<br />\n<br />\n當戴頭盔 帶防具出街變成日常，我地就等於成為義士嘅保護傘！<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾佢停！跟住落黎要行嘅路仲好長！我地要並肩作戰！<br />\n<br />\n已經有手足開始嘗試建立民安，但即時係普通和理非市民都有機會遇上危險！當我地大家都隨時有防具，就可以互相照應挺身而出！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部同我full gear返工！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348369</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLYjLfr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLYjLfr.png&h=5149521e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JYf22a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JYf22a.png&h=e9b74700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知每日好多事發生，有時會失焦，係時候返返正軌，討論跟住落黎嘅部署！"},{"pid":"f6ce8da6084433c2dc642640a07128ab626689f4","tid":1357374,"uid":20948,"li